- \cf4 Benhabib Wang 2013 JME: \cf0 model with financial constraint that generates indeterminacy of equilibria. In this context, shocks of all kinds produce boom-bust dynamics. Labor demand is effectively upward sloping and steeper than labor supply, this is due to the presence of an incentive compatibility constraint which gives pro cyclical lending, if one HH lends then also others are incentivized to do so, hence strategic complementarity in actions. \
