- \cf5 Azariadis Kaas Wen 2015 Restud: \cf6 falls into the category of self-fulfilling equilibria due to financial constraints as Benhabib Wang, Liu Wang. Make the distinction between secured and unsecured debt. Firms gain access to unsecured debt as expectations on future economic conditions improve which reduce incentives to default through the temporary loss of access to future credit. \
